name: Lincoln MKZ
selectionMessages: The Lincoln MKZ is designed to indulge your needs and reflect your taste for unique sophistication. With a brilliantly engineered, fully retractable panoramic roof; an interior that provides a multi-sensory experience of comfort and luxury; and human-centric technology throughout that anticipates your needs and provides ultimate control, the MKZ makes every journey more memorable.

features.description: The contrast of Foxfire red on jet black ignites a dramatic but elegant visual experience. Integrated with modern elements like striped trim and patterned, leather perforations, the stage is set for an unforgettable performance.
features.selectionMessage: You have selected Center Stage. A gorgeous interpretation of the ordinary, Center Stage puts the spotlight on those with a flair for the dramatic.
features.name: Center Stage

features.description: Natural, earthy tones create a relaxing atmosphere throughout the vehicle. Combined with the soft color and texture of our supple Venetian leather, Oasis creates a personal refuge far from the hustle and bustle of the world, purifying the mind and rejuvenating the soul.
features.selectionMessage: You have selected Oasis. A soothing sanctuary of cream and tan, Oasis speaks to those in pursuit of peace and tranquility.
features.name: Oasis

features.description: With a warm, coffee-color theme, Ganache and Truffle leathers are finished with an antiquing process that provides a rich, layered texture and creates a sensory experience that is both delicate and profound. Replete with thick, plush material.
features.selectionMessage: You have selected Indulgence. Few things ignite our senses like fine chocolate, the inspiration Indulgence: soft, rich, deep and sumptuous.
features.name: Indulgence

features.description: For those who appreciate a clean, modern aesthetic, look no further than this incredible theme. Featuring a high-contrast black-and-white interior highlighted by crimson stitching, this clean color scheme marries the artful past of Lincoln with the vision for its future.
features.selectionMessage: You have selected Modern Heritage. With a modern, minimalist aesthetic, Modern Heritage marries Lincoln¡¯s artful past to the vision for its future.
